{"title":"城市不衰——给香港","authors":["蓉子"],"dates":[{"year":1997,"month":6,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"城市不衰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——给香港"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓉子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"城市不衰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看见她日夜不熄的灯火和霓虹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从早到晚熙来攘往的脚步"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她永远她永远活力充沛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"急管繁弦的交响人杂市旺的闹忙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——只因为海在城内"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只因海在城内水流不歇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"城市不衰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"波涌浪卷地澎湃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因何我也喜欢那城市"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——她和我是亲是故"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还因她洋得地道又土得令我动心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而她流浪得已经够久了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即将回归"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"归去过她的后半生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是兴奋期盼抑或忧虑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那远远的童年足迹和原始的本真"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是否迎接她以无隔阂的笑靥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（作者系台湾著名诗人）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":11,"page_end":11}